  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rehabilitation of 117 spinal cord injury victims</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Spinal cord injury is very common among male in Karnataka due to falling from tamarind tree, coconut tree, and road traffic accidents. Unfortunately, most of the spinal cord injury people are the earning member of the family. Poverty is a major problem in spinal cord injury families. SRMAB CBR Project works in rural areas of Karnataka towards promoting inclusive development of persons with disabilities. The project provides a wheelchair, water bed, physiotherapy services, and necessary medicine.</narrative>
  </description>
